---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import BoardOfDirectorsCard from "../components/BoardOfDirectorsCard.astro";
import BoardOfAdvisorsCard from "../components/BoardOfAdvisorsCard.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Who we are">
  <div
    class="border-2 border-solid border-[#ABA1A1] rounded-lg p-6 shadow-2xl mb-7 text-slate-300 text-xl mx-6 bg-[#011c28]"
  >
    <h1
      class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-300 to-white text-transparent bg-clip-text text-7xl text-center border-b-2 border-solid border-[#ABA1A1]"
    >
      Who Are The ODevs?
    </h1>
    <section class="my-8">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row px-2 gap-6 items-center lg:items-center"
      >
        <div
          class="flex-1 lg:text-justify text-xl text-slate-200 order-2 lg:order-1 text-left"
        >
          <p>
            Orlando Devs is an Orlando-area wide community focused on growing
            and supporting developers at all levels to build their careers in
            Central Florida. Through the running of regular networking events,
            training sessions, hackathons, and collaboration events, Orlando
            Devs works to support developers in skill development and
            community-building. As a member of Innovate Orlando, the greater
            technology community of the Orlando area, Orlando Devs fosters
            collaboration between technologists, entrepreneurs, enterprise
            businesses, academia, and more. With a keen focus on growing
            diversity in the technology ecosystem, Orlando Devs supports
            programming that builds the talent pipeline for women and minorities
            in technology.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            Orlando Devs gives back to the community through mentorship, hosted
            events, and volunteerism to grow the tech community of Orlando.
            Orlando Devs is a 501(c)(3) non-profit organization.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <img
            src="/images/odevs-about.jpg"
            class="rounded-lg w-full order-1 lg:order-2"
            alt="ODevs"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <h1
        class="mt-16 text-center text-6xl bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-300 to-white text-transparent bg-clip-text"
      >
        Orlando Devs Board of Directors
      </h1>
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6 pt-16 justify-center">
        <BoardOfDirectorsCard />
      </div>
      <h1
        class="mt-16 text-center text-5xl bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-300 to-white text-transparent bg-clip-text"
      >
        Orlando Devs Board of Advisors
      </h1>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col flex-wrap lg:flex-row gap-6 pt-16 justify-center"
      >
        <BoardOfAdvisorsCard />
      </div>
      <h1
        class="mt-16 text-center text-4xl bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-300 to-white text-transparent bg-clip-text"
      >
        Former Orlando Devs Board Members
      </h1>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col text-center py-4 gap-y-4 text-2xl border-b-2 border-solid border-[#ABA1A1]"
      >
        <p>Cassandra Wilcox</p>
        <p>Jenell Pizarro</p>
        <p>Matt Burgess</p>
        <p>Jorge Hernandez</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-8 text-2xl text-center">
        <p>
          We hope that you will join us soon, be on the Orlando Devs Slack,
          Orlando Devs Meetup, or all the other software-related meetups
          happening in Orlando. Have a blast! ðŸš€
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
